snippet.title: Roly Poly Cannon: Bloody Monsters Pack
snippet.description: Roly Poly Cannon: Bloody Monsters Pack Destroy the monsters in a variety of ways by launching bombs at them.

snippet.title: Neptune Mahjong Connect
snippet.description: Neptune Mahjong Connect Puzzle game. Try to connect the tiles on each board but make sure the connection is free.

snippet.title: Monkey GO Happy: Mini Monkeys 2
snippet.description: Monkey GO Happy: Mini Monkeys 2 Puzzle game. Try to find all mini monkeys in as less clicks as possible!

snippet.title: Magi: The Fallen World
snippet.description: Magi: The Fallen World RPG adventure. Pick a character and look for quests, explore dungeons and fight powerful monsters.

snippet.title: Laser Cannon 2
snippet.description: Laser Cannon 2 Use your laser canon to shoot all monsters in each level. Get rid of objects that are in the way.

snippet.title: Monkey GO Happy: Mini Monkeys
snippet.description: Monkey GO Happy: Mini Monkeys Puzzle game. Use as less clicks possible to retrieve each of the 15 mini monkeys.

snippet.title: Bit Dungeon
snippet.description: Bit Dungeon Dungeon adventure. Find a way out of the dungeon and rescue your wife who is trapped in there.

snippet.title: Pocket Platoon
snippet.description: Pocket Platoon Strategy game. Build and guide an epic platoon into battle zones to destroy the alien units.

snippet.title: Monster Legions
snippet.description: Monster Legions Strategy game. Go to battle and use cards to pick the right type of warriors as the battle must be won.

snippet.title: Bloons Super Monkey
snippet.description: Bloons Super Monkey Take control of the Super Monkey from Bloons Tower Defense in an epic arcade shooter.
